<plot>A look at the people and events that demonstrated "the vitality of the American spirit". This program reported stories on some of the lesser-known, but nonetheless uplifting happenings from around the country. With Bill Moyers presenting more serious subjects, and Charles Kuralt and Art Buchwald giving their take on the less serious scenes of American life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?540085</url></doc>
